The formulas for Δ and Σ given here are similar to those presented in Strand et al. (2014), with some key differences as follows: (i) those in Strand et al. (2014) are derived for models that have M1 and M2 in both equations for (3) and (4); (ii) formulas given in the Appendix of Strand et al. (2014) do not include covariates, although non-interactive covariates were generally considered in that article. (Including non-interactive covariates would essentially involve replacing 
 with (
) for every occurrence in Σγ, Σθγ, and Σπγ, based on notation used in that article; note also that conditioning on Zi in formulas was suppressed part-way through that article for convenience.)
